{"tid":2338473,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"觀塘塞車塞到有情緒病　巴打搞「每日屌官塘老母」專頁：希望更多人憎觀塘","createTime":"2020-12-24T04:47:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T08:00:46.000Z","uid":271829,"like":14,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5da034cf9b88e490a321175d36ab30dae8bfaf5a","tid":2338473,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T04:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/gif20_BrkLX_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fgif20_BrkLX_1200x0.jpg&h=934bd799&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n版主製作的迷因圖。（圖片來自「每日屌官塘老母」專頁）<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n觀塘出名交通擠塞，上下班時間儼如「動物大遷徒」，塞車一、兩小時起跳，網民叮囑放工「水都唔好飲多滴」，以免被困車上無法如廁。曾在觀塘上班的浩然（化名），下班試過用兩小時才回到荃灣，「真係好撚柒憎觀塘」，上月在 Facebook 開設「每日屌官塘老母」專頁及群組，與網民一同出力「問候」觀塘母親，發洩對觀塘的不滿。<br />\n從觀塘道、開源道、走到駿業街，浩然無一不「問候」。他製作的迷因圖「你再叫我去一次觀塘，我就讓你上靈堂」、「Over the Hoi Yuen Road」等等，不少人都表示很有共鳴，亦在群組大呻塞車及街道不潔等問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/491948425116070/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F491948425116070%2F&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=91a9c0e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/491948425116070/</a><br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/images/觀塘塞車塞到有情緒病-巴打搞-每日屌官塘老母-專頁-希望更多人憎觀塘/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fimages%2F%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E5%A1%9E%E8%BB%8A%E5%A1%9E%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%89%E6%83%85%E7%B7%92%E7%97%85-%E5%B7%B4%E6%89%93%E6%90%9E-%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E5%B1%8C%E5%AE%98%E5%A1%98%E8%80%81%E6%AF%8D-%E5%B0%88%E9%A0%81-%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E6%86%8E%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%2F&d=otIFGLHjmDp%2FicXUVK76MYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=55f78a42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fimages%2F%E8%A7%80%E5%A1%98%E5%A1%9E%E8%BB%8A%E5%A1%9E%E5%88%B0%E6%9C%89%